 Michelle Jackson, the ex-wife of popular music promoter and MAVIN boss, Don Jazzy, has fondly recounted their time together. During an interview, the US-based Nigerian pointed out how she enjoyed being married to Don Jazzy despite occasional conflicts and misunderstandings. “We were so carefree and happy, I don’t think we had so much baggage that maybe I would have now. “It was just fun and of course, every relationship has its ups and downs. We’d probably fight a while and then we would be cool again. “Honestly I know that at that particular age, there were so many things that could have gone wrong, but for the most part of our marriage a lot of things went right and we were just cool, we were easy. “He’s very down to earth, very cool. We flowed mehn, we flowed.”